title: I changed my sim card from my old pixel to new pixel 5. Oops, maybe I shouldn't have? No 5g.
content: I changed my sim card from my old pixel to new pixel 5. Oops, maybe I shouldn't have? No 5g. What's the risk of using the new sim that came with the Pixel 5, any thoughts?
